{
  "stem": "24885.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the other half, we used to go home for lunch, because our big meal was always at noon, 1:00 or 2:00.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we'd go back and have Hebrew lessons and classes and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Approximately in 1938, my mother decided that I should also get a better education and in a Talmud.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when my father started the business, at first-- I say when they started because he had the business before '28 approximately when he came to Radom.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was on the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in either in '29 or '30, from-- we start to be modern.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From the factories, he got what we call in German [GERMAN], a franchise from a certain factory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he sold only their goods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He sold it to shoe makers, to shoe factories, anybody who could use.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And only the soft leather, not the hard leather.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He sold it to anybody who could use this type of material.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then when my mother took over, the man by this point-- for reasons I don't remember-- left.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she got somebody either more capable or so on, a local man from the city that we knew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he worked with her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we were kids.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were all busy going to school, going to cheder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The few hours we had at night to play with our friends and Shabbas.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Naturally, Shabbas was observed 100%, not like-- not like here, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody in the city of Radom, there were approximately close to 30,000 Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The city, at this time, had a population total of between 110 and 120 with outlying area-- Christians, no.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "30,000 Families.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm almost sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, we had a lot of Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a lot of temples and a lot of shuls.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
